1
00:00:43,060 --> 00:00:46,780
=Auspicious Nobles=

2
00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:49,940
=Episode 17=

3
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:52,500
(The Crown Prince vs. Li Qingqing)

4
00:00:59,920 --> 00:01:01,520
(The Tower Master of Wangshi Tower.)

5
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:29,590
Qing...

6
00:01:30,040 --> 00:01:31,280
Qingqing.

7
00:01:31,870 --> 00:01:32,310
You...

8
00:01:32,430 --> 00:01:33,310
Your Highness.

9
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:35,480
Do I look good in this outfit?

10
00:01:36,430 --> 00:01:38,840
This style is popular
in the Capital lately.

11
00:01:39,070 --> 00:01:41,920
They say it blocks the sun
and has a unique charm.

12
00:01:47,310 --> 00:01:48,870
(Thank goodness it's not her.)

13
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:00,790
Beautiful.

14
00:02:03,950 --> 00:02:06,150
Your Highness,
when you looked at me just now,

15
00:02:06,150 --> 00:02:08,030
you seemed rather surprised.

16
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:09,710
Don't tell me

17
00:02:09,870 --> 00:02:12,840
you mistook me for
the Tower Master of Wangshi Tower.

18
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:28,310
Are you?

19
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:36,310
I was only joking.

20
00:02:37,310 --> 00:02:39,800
How could you be
the Tower Master of Wangshi Tower?

21
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:45,150
Lately,

22
00:02:45,470 --> 00:02:46,910
Father has been displeased with me.

23
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:50,400
You should avoid
getting too close to me,

24
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:52,630
so you won't be implicated.

25
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:13,030
(Why is he still worried about me now?)

26
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:21,430
(Li Qingqing.)

27
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:22,840
(Get a hold of yourself.)

28
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:25,560
(Ruining someone's wealth
is like killing their parents.)

29
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:53,870
Your Majesty,

30
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:55,630
I have solid evidence.

31
00:03:55,630 --> 00:03:57,030
Someone saw with their own eyes

32
00:03:57,030 --> 00:03:59,590
the Tower Master
entering the Inspectorate yesterday.

33
00:03:59,750 --> 00:04:00,240
This proves

34
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:02,840
the rumors in the Capital
are not baseless.

35
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:04,710
The Crown Prince and that rebel

36
00:04:04,710 --> 00:04:06,560
are indeed involved.

37
00:04:06,870 --> 00:04:07,710
Absurd.

38
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:10,150
The Crown Prince
personally pursued the Tower Master.

39
00:04:10,150 --> 00:04:11,680
How could he be involved with her?

40
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:14,360
Official Wang,

41
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:15,360
are you implying

42
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:17,390
that the Crown Prince

43
00:04:17,390 --> 00:04:20,390
deliberately accused the Second Prince
of colluding with the Tower Master?

44
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:22,000
Isn't that obvious?

45
00:04:22,870 --> 00:04:23,720
Yuanzhao,

46
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:25,070
what do you think?

47
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:28,070
Father, I don't know.

48
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:30,680
But Yuanhe isn't that kind of person.

49
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,430
Once may be a coincidence.

50
00:04:34,950 --> 00:04:36,360
But twice? Three times?

51
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,310
Could they still be coincidences?

52
00:04:39,510 --> 00:04:40,270
Issue my decree.

53
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:43,630
The Crown Prince will remain confined
to reflect on his actions.

54
00:04:44,750 --> 00:04:45,920
Yuanzhao,

55
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,920
well done.

56
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:53,190
Your Highness, when Miss Qingqing
dressed like that last time,

57
00:04:53,300 --> 00:04:54,660
was it really just a coincidence?

58
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:57,800
Qingqing...

59
00:05:03,330 --> 00:05:04,270
Your Highness, look out!

60
00:05:04,390 --> 00:05:04,830
Go!

61
00:05:16,430 --> 00:05:16,950
After them!

62
00:05:20,430 --> 00:05:22,240
It's that expert
by the Tower Master's side.

63
00:05:22,530 --> 00:05:24,890
The Tower Master of Wangshi Tower
has become far too brazen.

64
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:32,720
You scoundrel!

65
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,920
I even gave you advice before.

66
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:36,040
What an ungrateful wretch.

67
00:05:36,270 --> 00:05:38,480
Pretty boys as calculating as you

68
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:40,430
always meet a miserable end.

69
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:42,630
If you keep going against Wangshi Tower,

70
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:44,240
I'll throw you out of the Eastern Palace

71
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:46,680
and send you
to a pleasure house to serve tea.

72
00:06:01,450 --> 00:06:03,990
That trained assassin by her side
uses an unpredictable sword style.

73
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:04,950
As long as he's there,

74
00:06:05,280 --> 00:06:06,600
even if we find the Tower Master,

75
00:06:06,610 --> 00:06:08,550
we won't be able
to get close enough to kill her.

76
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:10,070
Once you find her whereabouts,

77
00:06:11,870 --> 00:06:13,000
don't rush to kill her.

78
00:06:14,750 --> 00:06:16,750
Keep her under watch for me.

79
00:06:17,430 --> 00:06:17,830
Yes.

80
00:06:24,630 --> 00:06:27,240
Following the marks
you secretly left behind,

81
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:28,360
we found that workshop.

82
00:06:28,870 --> 00:06:30,800
We discovered thousands of siege weapons

83
00:06:31,070 --> 00:06:33,430
and tens of thousands
of military weapons.

84
00:06:35,190 --> 00:06:36,070
Perfect.

85
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:38,040
They'll all be mine to use.

86
00:06:39,500 --> 00:06:42,220
(Wangshi Workshop)

87
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:43,160
Everyone,

88
00:06:43,750 --> 00:06:45,750
you've all worked hard
these past few days.

89
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:47,680
Today is payday.

90
00:06:48,270 --> 00:06:50,720
You'll receive this month's
and next month's wages.

91
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:53,950
Everyone will also get
an extra month's bonus.

92
00:06:55,510 --> 00:06:59,240
- Great!
- Great!

93
00:06:59,950 --> 00:07:01,160
Mine!

94
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:03,430
All right, everyone.
Line up to collect your pay.

95
00:07:05,310 --> 00:07:07,070
Me first!

96
00:07:07,070 --> 00:07:08,240
Finally, it's payday!

97
00:07:08,630 --> 00:07:09,720
Assassin Number One,

98
00:07:12,190 --> 00:07:13,040
this is yours.

99
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:16,920
See?

100
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:19,600
Working for me
has its perks, doesn't it?

101
00:07:20,750 --> 00:07:21,920
Where's my dead seagull?

102
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:25,590
You mean the Chief Financial Officer?

103
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:27,270
Fine.

104
00:07:29,630 --> 00:07:30,120
Next.

105
00:07:31,190 --> 00:07:33,360
I officially appoint you

106
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:35,270
(CFO Jiuzhu)
as the Chief Financial Officer of Wangshi Tower.

107
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:37,190
You're messing with me!

108
00:07:40,190 --> 00:07:42,040
Who's messing with you?

109
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:43,560
Next!

110
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:45,040
(CFO Jiuzhu)
This little badge

111
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:47,240
means a three hundred tael raise.

112
00:07:48,060 --> 00:07:49,340
(CFO Jiuzhu)

113
00:07:50,510 --> 00:07:52,800
If you don't want it,
I'll give it to Caiyuan.

114
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:54,430
Sure!

115
00:07:55,620 --> 00:07:56,260
(CFO Jiuzhu)

116
00:08:01,510 --> 00:08:02,480
Next!

117
00:08:05,870 --> 00:08:06,600
Here. Thanks.

118
00:08:06,750 --> 00:08:07,390
This is yours.

119
00:08:07,390 --> 00:08:08,260
(CFO Jiuzhu)

120
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:10,870
Keep up the good work.

121
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,800
Making money is hard work.

122
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:14,300
I need some snacks to keep me going.

123
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:15,720
Run an errand for me.

124
00:08:16,420 --> 00:08:18,240
Sunflower seeds
from Old Lady Wang's on East Street.

125
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:19,720
Candied hawthorns
from Li's Shop in the West Market.

126
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:21,360
And two taels' worth of savory pancakes.

127
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:24,510
Would you like your pancakes spicy?

128
00:08:25,270 --> 00:08:26,070
Extra spicy.

129
00:08:30,290 --> 00:08:31,160
Keep up the good work.

130
00:08:35,510 --> 00:08:37,320
It feels great to have money.

131
00:08:37,630 --> 00:08:40,000
I can even boss people around
without feeling guilty.

132
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:41,790
All right.

133
00:08:46,510 --> 00:08:47,270
Here you go.

134
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:56,790
Thank you.

135
00:08:57,390 --> 00:08:58,120
Two plain ones.

136
00:08:58,120 --> 00:08:58,870
I'll take two.

137
00:08:59,120 --> 00:08:59,870
Jiuzhu.

138
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:01,620
The greatest assassin in Great Yong.

139
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:03,390
He once commanded
three hundred trained assassins,

140
00:09:03,390 --> 00:09:04,780
and founded the Shadow Organization.

141
00:09:04,790 --> 00:09:07,210
He carried out countless secret
kill orders throughout the realm.

142
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:10,120
Then, three years ago,
he suddenly vanished.

143
00:09:10,510 --> 00:09:11,670
No one knew where he had gone.

144
00:09:11,870 --> 00:09:13,030
Nor did anyone know why.

145
00:09:13,190 --> 00:09:13,960
Two taels' worth.

146
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:15,360
Extra spicy.

147
00:09:16,190 --> 00:09:16,870
Coming right up.

148
00:09:18,870 --> 00:09:20,720
That thing looks familiar.

149
00:09:21,550 --> 00:09:22,270
Get it.

150
00:09:22,870 --> 00:09:23,840
Don't tip them off.

151
00:09:24,550 --> 00:09:24,840
Yes.

152
00:09:26,670 --> 00:09:27,480
Here you go.

153
00:09:39,980 --> 00:09:42,060
(Ledger)

154
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:44,360
Yuanzhao's side

155
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:45,720
brings the total

156
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:47,270
to forty million taels.

157
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:49,510
The bank
can finally start issuing loans.

158
00:09:49,630 --> 00:09:51,080
Just one month's interest

159
00:09:51,080 --> 00:09:53,550
should bring in
hundreds of thousands of taels.

160
00:09:54,870 --> 00:09:56,440
I finally...

161
00:10:01,870 --> 00:10:03,720
Next time you come in,
could you knock first?

162
00:10:04,670 --> 00:10:06,750
What if I wasn't dressed?

163
00:10:07,500 --> 00:10:08,930
There wouldn't be much to see anyway.

164
00:10:12,590 --> 00:10:13,600
What are you looking at?

165
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:18,000
What is it?

166
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,840
Didn't we just get paid today?

167
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,200
My little goal is gone.

168
00:10:22,030 --> 00:10:22,590
Your Highness,

169
00:10:23,150 --> 00:10:24,600
we recovered this

170
00:10:24,610 --> 00:10:26,270
from Jiuzhu, the Tower Master's
trained assassin.

171
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:34,120
Your Highness.

172
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:43,840
Is this item sold anywhere?

173
00:10:43,850 --> 00:10:45,120
We've searched the entire Capital.

174
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:46,000
Every shop.

175
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:46,750
Every market stall.

176
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:48,030
No one sells it.

177
00:10:48,360 --> 00:10:49,720
It must be a token

178
00:10:50,030 --> 00:10:51,000
unique to Wangshi Tower.

179
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:56,670
(Li Qingqing...)

180
00:10:57,910 --> 00:10:59,630
(Could you also be
part of Wangshi Tower?)

181
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:01,510
(Or...)

182
00:11:02,480 --> 00:11:04,000
(Are you the Tower Master?)

183
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:05,870
So you're saying,

184
00:11:05,870 --> 00:11:07,750
when you went to buy pancakes,

185
00:11:08,030 --> 00:11:09,600
you ran into the Crown Prince's men?

186
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:17,600
I'm done for.

187
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:19,510
He must have figured out it was me.

188
00:11:23,670 --> 00:11:25,150
He only suspects me.

189
00:11:25,150 --> 00:11:26,340
He doesn't have any proof yet.

190
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:29,080
Judging by his unusual behavior lately,

191
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:32,120
he's unlikely to kill me outright.

192
00:11:32,510 --> 00:11:35,240
At least, with the way
he's thinking now,

193
00:11:35,910 --> 00:11:37,960
he shouldn't kill me

194
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:39,840
until he's completely certain.

195
00:11:40,290 --> 00:11:41,200
What kind of thinking?

196
00:11:42,510 --> 00:11:43,630
A lovestruck fool.

197
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:46,320
He summoned me...

198
00:11:46,870 --> 00:11:47,320
What?

199
00:11:49,270 --> 00:11:49,960
He...

200
00:11:50,670 --> 00:11:51,910
He likes me.

201
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:56,550
Hey!

202
00:11:57,320 --> 00:11:59,390
What are you laughing at,
you bamboo stick?

203
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:00,440
Nothing.

204
00:12:01,120 --> 00:12:02,080
As long as you're happy.

205
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:04,550
Who likes him?

206
00:12:04,790 --> 00:12:06,840
That's just my analysis.

207
00:12:08,270 --> 00:12:10,120
Nothing ventured, nothing gained.

208
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:11,150
I can't run away anyway.

209
00:12:11,150 --> 00:12:12,390
I can only take the risk.

210
00:12:27,510 --> 00:12:28,080
Your Highness,

211
00:12:28,790 --> 00:12:30,000
the assassins are in position.

212
00:12:30,630 --> 00:12:31,870
If Li Qingqing is in danger

213
00:12:32,120 --> 00:12:33,000
and Jiuzhu appears,

214
00:12:33,180 --> 00:12:34,590
then she must be the Tower Master.

215
00:12:42,600 --> 00:12:43,480
Miss.

216
00:12:48,080 --> 00:12:48,750
Stay calm.

217
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:50,550
Your Highness, shall we make our move?

218
00:13:10,320 --> 00:13:11,150
Do it.

219
00:13:17,510 --> 00:13:20,870
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

220
00:13:21,630 --> 00:13:25,030
♪Your dark hair
brushes across my fingertips♪

221
00:13:25,790 --> 00:13:27,550
♪Your smile♪

222
00:13:27,790 --> 00:13:30,070
♪Melts away the winter snow♪

223
00:13:30,070 --> 00:13:33,750
♪One fleeting glance says more
than a thousand words♪

224
00:13:34,230 --> 00:13:37,550
♪Yet I stand before you♪

225
00:13:38,270 --> 00:13:42,110
♪Unable to recognize your eyes♪

226
00:13:42,510 --> 00:13:44,430
♪Though fate tries♪

227
00:13:44,430 --> 00:13:47,030
♪To make us pass each other by♪

228
00:13:47,230 --> 00:13:50,670
♪I choose to make our story whole♪

229
00:13:50,910 --> 00:13:52,550
♪Though time slips by♪

230
00:13:52,550 --> 00:13:54,310
♪As day turns into night♪

231
00:13:54,830 --> 00:13:58,870
♪I still remember
our days at Wangshi Tower♪

232
00:13:59,270 --> 00:14:01,670
♪One glance at you lasts a lifetime♪

233
00:14:01,670 --> 00:14:03,430
♪Blessed by fate♪

234
00:14:03,430 --> 00:14:08,590
♪I believe this moment
will last forever♪

235
00:14:08,590 --> 00:14:11,030
♪Your smiling face♪

236
00:14:11,030 --> 00:14:13,870
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

237
00:14:13,870 --> 00:14:17,510
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

238
00:14:18,030 --> 00:14:21,470
♪And wander the world together♪

239
00:14:21,470 --> 00:14:22,830
♪Holding you close♪

240
00:14:22,830 --> 00:14:25,350
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

241
00:14:25,350 --> 00:14:27,670
♪Your tenderness♪

242
00:14:27,670 --> 00:14:30,550
♪Is the brightest moon♪

243
00:14:30,550 --> 00:14:34,230
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

244
00:14:34,750 --> 00:14:38,070
♪Our love will never fade away♪

245
00:14:38,070 --> 00:14:40,510
♪Though heaven and earth grow old♪

246
00:14:41,030 --> 00:14:45,310
♪My heart will remain forever pure♪

247
00:14:54,790 --> 00:14:56,950
♪Your smiling face♪

248
00:14:57,110 --> 00:14:59,710
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

249
